  "description": "Lambda function fleet view: invocations, errors, duration percentiles, throttles, concurrent executions, async event age, init duration. Reads CloudWatch metrics in the AWS/Lambda namespace via the CloudWatch data source. Use as the entry dashboard for serverless workloads.",
